reviews.review_text: Recording Info Neumann KM140 mics -> Aerco pre-amp -> Sony  D-10 Pro. FOB. Mics in mesh baseball hat. Recorded by Dominic Tringale and Roger Jones. Maybe Jim Cowen and Keith Litzenberger we're with us. I don't remember
